## Recipe

1. Slice vertically to the side of the seed
1. Peel off the skin around the piece with the seed. Slice off small pieces and use a spoon to scrape off remaining fruit from the seed
1. On the thin piece, slice vertically, then scoop out the pieces with a spoon
